title.narrative: Haiti - Urban Community Driven Development Project / PRODEPUR

description.narrative: To improve access to, and satisfaction with: (i) basic and social infrastructure and services, including housing repair, reconstruction and community infrastructure improvements needed as a result of the Emergency; and (ii) income-generating opportunities for residents of selected disadvantaged urban areas.

condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :3.01 | Description :The Recipient declares its commitment to the objective of the Project, and shall cause theProject to be carried out by BMPAD in accordance with the provisions of Article IV of the General Conditions. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :3.02 | Description :The Recipient shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordnace with the provisionsof Schedule 2 to this Agreement. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :5.03 | Description :the Effectiveness Deadline is the date ninety days (90) days after the date of thisAgreement | Due Date :21-Feb-2011

Finance Agreement :ARTICLE V — EFFECTIVENESS; TERMINATION | Description :The Subsidiary Agreement has been entered into between theRecipient and BMPAD, in a manner acceptable to the Association, and it has been duly authorized or ratified by the Recipient andBMPAD and is legally binding upon both parties in accordance with its terms. | Due Date :30-Sep-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :No later than six (6) months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shallhaveprepared and disclosed the Resettlement Policy Framework | Due Date :03-Feb-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure that a specialist is selected andappointed to carry out the baseline survey for the Project, no later than one month after the Effective Date. | Due Date:27-Nov-2008

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure that a technical auditor isselected and appointed no later than 3 months after the Effective Date. | Due Date :27-Jan-2009

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure that not later than 3 monthsafter the Effective Date, a technical auditor is selected | Due Date :21-Apr-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure that not later than two (2)months after the Effective Date, at least one Service Agreement is concluded by BMPAD | Due Date :21-Apr-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure that technical audits are carriedout by an independent auditor semi-annually. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to ensure thath a baseline survey iscarried out no later than 6 months after the Effective Date. | Due Date :27-Apr-2009
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to enter into an agreement (serviceagreement) with each eligible MDOD. | Due Date :01-Jun-2009
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to maintain the Operational Manual. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to: no later than one (1) month aftertheEffective Date, update the POM for the purpose of the Project | Due Date :21-Mar-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD through its PCU to monitor and evaluatethe progress of the Project and to prepare Project Reports. | Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD to appoint, no later than 4 months afterthe Effective Date, an independent auditor. | Due Date :27-Feb-2009

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II | Description :The Recipient shall cause BMPAD, through the PCU, to prepare and furnishto IDA interim unaudited financial reports, no later than 45 days after the end of each calendar quarter. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II | Description :The Recipient shall maintain for itself and cause to be maintained inBMPAD a financial management system in accordance with Section 4.09 of the General Conditions. | Frequency :Yearly
